less (view and search text files) (man uses less)

command -options(over 30) arguments(file)

-2 options
--help - view a summary of less commands and navigation
-N - view line numbers



Why is less important? - default pages for man pages, viewing text is an essential task in linux.

less --help

less video5.txt
q

less -N video5.txt (numbers line, especially helpful reviewing code)

tip - footer of less reminds you of 2 most important keys (h - help, q - quit)
